# Local dev tooling only. NONE of this belongs in the repo.
#
# package.json in particular is deliberately NOT committed: Cloudflare Pages auto-detects a
# package.json and would start running a build step for a site that has none. The site is
# plain static files and must stay that way. tools/chrome-snapshot.mjs needs playwright, so
# install it locally when you want to run it:
#
#     npm i -D playwright && npx playwright install chromium
#
node_modules/
package.json
package-lock.json
